    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wishlist GRIMWHIMSY to get news about the game.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057040/extras/133db20a5221b506865c2a6aa7d46d9e.poster.avif?t=1769029995\" width=604 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057040/extras/133db20a5221b506865c2a6aa7d46d9e.webm?t=1769029995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057040/extras/133db20a5221b506865c2a6aa7d46d9e.mp4?t=1769029995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057040/extras/250a6f260b9784de07314a63dd435984.avif?t=1769029995\" width=600 height=119 /></span><br><br><strong>准备好迎接恐怖和笑声吧！</strong> 你和你的朋友是被扔进一个被遗忘的实验室的黑暗和危险的走廊中的罪犯。你们的任务是生存下来并发现这些恐怖地方发生了什么。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057040/extras/7e0cf338e77fc6c46d4a7dcf9beccb64.avif?t=1769029995\" width=600 height=119 /></span><br><strong>这些走廊的每个角落都充满了秘密和危险。</strong> 保持警惕，每一步都可能是最后一步。利用光和影来欺骗怪物并继续前进。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057040/extras/43c96d93d1f5287a6270864ffe33da64.avif?t=1769029995\" width=600 height=119 /></span><br><strong>程序生成的关卡</strong> 使每场游戏都独一无二。收集资源，修理设备并避开陷阱。通过文本和语音聊天与朋友沟通，制定策略并互相帮助生存。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057040/extras/d0cfbc6116b6efccc3c5be1d1ff84878.avif?t=1769029995\" width=600 height=119 /></span><br><strong>特别的恐慌点系统</strong> 让你通过与怪物的遭遇和完成任务来赚取积分。这些积分可以在飞行邮筒中兑换有价值的物品，帮助你生存。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057040/extras/e669d73cb16b3f0880781a52b36ce81b.avif?t=1769029995\" width=600 height=119 /></span><br><strong>准备好面对有趣和荒谬的情况吧：</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><i>当你在治疗时，怪物吃掉了你的朋友？这是向政府报告并获得积分的绝佳机会！</i><br></li><li><i>你的朋友拿走了你的战利品？别担心，你可以随时用电击枪让他瘫痪，或者把他交给怪物吃。</i></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057040/extras/c2cbc8a5633f084401c698f5aefa8062.avif?t=1769029995\" width=600 height=119 /></span><br><strong>这是一个关于恐惧、生存和在一切都出错时的笑声的游戏。</strong> 你能生存下来并揭开被遗弃的实验室的所有秘密吗？自己去发现吧，但别忘了你的朋友——还有谁会分散怪物的注意力呢？！<br><br><i>这就是朋友的作用，不是吗？至少在我们的实验室里是这样的！</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057040/extras/04b75b90340ff00b7f3cd6a4db823264.poster.avif?t=1769029995\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057040/extras/04b75b90340ff00b7f3cd6a4db823264.webm?t=1769029995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057040/extras/04b75b90340ff00b7f3cd6a4db823264.mp4?t=1769029995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
